strings: <voice_0x01000E30><se_low>*: Use! Somebody take this crown from me!
<voice_0x01000E31><se_low>*: I'm right here, okay? I lie at your feet!
<voice_0x01000E32><se_low>*: I started to dive into the well. But I fell and I can't get out! please help me!
<voice_0x01000E33><se_low>*: take my crown and marry me You have to give him water though! Make it rain!
<voice_0x01000E37><se_low>*: Change your point of view! could you help me now?
<voice_0x01000E34><se_low>*: Thank you, you should just break my crown! I'm happy. move tough!
<voice_0x01000E35><se_high>*: Unbelievable ! The funny wreath is ready. Here is your victory! (Aperitif)
